Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...it would be easy if we could question\Nthe mastermind behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Mastermind...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You're referring to that girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl you met in the\Nwhite room, right Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:26.11,Main,,0,0,0,,But, to get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...someone needs to become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We're not going that route!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's think of another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I... have no wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a wish now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to release her\Nfrom the card. My friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,My precious friends...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to meet Tama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--That wish may come true...\N--If you battle again,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,--That wish may come true...\N--there's no telling what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,--Something worse may happen next!\N--no telling what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The Selector battles are full of lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,There could be more behind all this...\NI need to be careful with my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:17.99,Main,,0,0,0,,But, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...I won't be able to move, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:44.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all because of that strange voice of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}? How about a game of WIXOSS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma made a new deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,So, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that kind of\NLRIG card was released...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, the effect is pretty neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}, your LRIG was Tama-{\i1}chan{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.52,Main,,0,0,0,,T-Tama is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm... actually trying a new deck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me try this LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you using me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't a battle between Selectors,\Nso there shouldn't be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, since we don't have any tangerines,\Nwhat penalty should we play on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.87,Main,,0,0,0,,How about grocery shopping\Nfor tonight's dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,So, disregarding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can disregard me forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish will come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. She's here... in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, you're that model, Akira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Wow, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You appeared in {\i1}Men's Lon-Lon{\i0}\Nas a model before, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut it, twerp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Kept you waiting there, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? I-Iona...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:03.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be spouting that crap's name\Nwith that crap voice of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Not against my Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Urith...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You promised not to say that name in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't put makeup on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to praise me, Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Because of Urith, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...was finally able to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up, old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't bother me, and get\Nwhoever that is out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want me to be in the public eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.18,Main,,0,0,0,,bring me the money\NI need to get this face fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira! Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Missus? Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The editor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We came for you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't need me anymore, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, there's no way\Nyou'd need me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:28.01,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a request by a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Certain someone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Back then, I closed my heart from everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But, for some reason...\Nit was as if I was guided...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,See? Looking good as ever, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, you've got that sexy edge on you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me get someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,So is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You set this up to get some\Nlaughs seeing me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what's this about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Making a fool out of me?!\NI'm gonna scar your face just like mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Please scar me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's what it takes...\Nto mend your scarred heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That damn, stuck up LRIG...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona... isn't here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I was told by Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,The rules governing the world of Selectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:15.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...and that Iona's wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That's messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:27.59,Main,,0,0,0,,So, regardless of my wish, Iona wanted\Nto quit being a human all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need for me to hide this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,If... If only she wasn't around, then I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I’ve always longed for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Even when I was Iona's LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Lemme go! After all that\Ncrap you said about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to rouse yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The negative emotions you\Nbore made you a better person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to let loose...\Nyour inner emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Your beauty is one that\Ncan't be tainted by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Neither by Iona, or by WIXOSS...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,That scar is proof of your passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's more beautiful and\Nprecious than all there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:37.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Even after, Urith kept her eyes on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Old hag! How many times do I have to\Ntell you to say that you're coming in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,This box was addressed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,"Urazoe Iona"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This... A makeup kit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira, we wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You were out for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you e-mail us?\NWe missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a lot easier than expected,\Ngoing out again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? A commercial?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona asked for you, Akira-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nto appear with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you up to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:10:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I hated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I hated Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not smart, and I'm poor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I had confidence in my looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I was always the center of attention,\Neven as a model...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:34.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But, ever since Iona appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...no matter how I dress, or how I pose,\Nall everyone sees is Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just a foil for Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so frustrated...\NNo one was looking at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The 2012...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,..."Valentine's Day Special" edition page.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Add 20% More Makeup To Your Eyes\NWithout Being Busted By Your Teacher;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Natural Makeup Lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,That was your first appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Next is the 2012\N"Summer Of Excitement" edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,In the article featuring\Npersonal belongings, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you that I always admired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that stalkerish?\NDoes that make you feel weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,But... these are my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:29.75,Main,,0,0,0,,As Urazoe Iona, I'll use all her wealth and\Nconnections to make your wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,To have more people look upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:37.51,Main,,0,0,0,,To get to a level not even\NIona could have achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:38.59,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to... see you shine in brilliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I had someone who loved me this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... I didn't know that love\Ncould make me so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You got rid of the bad\NAki-lucky inside of me, Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lucky is now Aki-lovely\Nbecause of you, Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lovely...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:25.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Did the hatred you have\Ntowards Iona disappear already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Was that all there was to your passion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:34.65,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if you'll love me, Urith, then I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,The negative emotions you bore\Nmade you a better person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the very reason why I\Nshower you freely with my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira, can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...listen to my request?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... Carrots... Potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Carrots" "Potatoes" "Onions" "Chicken" "Curry"\NUm... Carrots... Potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, and that's two bags of\Npotatoes with five in each.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww... That's mean, Grandma!\NWhy make so much curry now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? It wouldn't be much of a penalty\Nif the shopping load was light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Kominato--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, did you see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It was Akira! She appeared in\Nthis month's {\i1}Ron-Ron {\i0}magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Her scar's gone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she became a Selector again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,And then maybe her wish came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... That's good to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It isn't good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nis looking for Selectors again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Selectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, well... now's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's meet tomorrow. Okay... See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yup. Well, I'll go shopping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Your "happy" is gonna run away\Nwith that long face of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That was Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith is an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.77,Main,,0,0,0,,She has a mission to fulfill, for my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona's wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it to be my LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That's only part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish is to become an LRIG\Nto a skilled Selector, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.57,Main,,0,0,0,,...to find another skilled Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Ru-ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You, too, Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Do Not Enter"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:15.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup! I got another deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, I got the rights to\Nbecome a Selector again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say hi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi there, I'm Milulun!\NPleased to meet you-lunlun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait... Why do you want to battle again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lucky is unlucky now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I can hide my scar with makeup,\NI can't make it go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Secretly hiding it for\Nthe rest of my life is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor, Akira. Sobby-sobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if Ru-ru can battle me,\NI feel like I can do my best again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:17:00.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Ru-ru. Battle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:19.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know Iona, or Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}'s intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey... looks like you're a real LRIG now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Wanted to be an LRIG, eh?\NTwisted, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:56.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Let Aki-lucky teach a pervy girl\Nlike you a thing or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Milulun, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Ruko going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:10.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You know how reckless Akira is\Nwhen it comes to battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:14.39,Main,,0,0,0,,If there's a battle, without Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of girl Tama was like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Before turning into an LRIG,\NTama was like any other girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:28.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Kind of hard to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,At first, she was like just\Nsaying "nyaah," and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,But... she is Ruko's precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,So weak...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon, Babel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko... are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,My ability forces the opponent to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:19:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,In this turn, it makes strategic sense\Nto summon a high-powered SIGNI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Why the heck is an LRIG giving orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:14.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm... not serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:20.74,Main,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Spell! Slash Miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Here comes a spell! Milulun! Anti-Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Miiiilulun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You girls! Didn't you see the sign\Nthat said "Do Not Enter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Now hurry and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Interrupted in the middle of battle again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Super pathetic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,After all you went through to be an LRIG,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.71,Main,,0,0,0,,you end up being stuck with\Na wimpy Selector like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You think you can get away\Nwith just one battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:24.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll just keep coming back over and\Nover again to make life miserable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...for the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye-lun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Serious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's... not that I wasn't serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But, it isn't fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not with friends or with Tama,\Nso this isn't fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yippieeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what they were saying was true then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I was kind of worried whether\NI should have told you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,There is this thing about\Nconfidentiality, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! What should I do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Eldora? If I become a card,\Ncan I choose what I'll wear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori's gonna definitely\Nchoose something all in pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,And... mint-green is cool, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Thought you said "definitely"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori! "That's Moonlight Chorizo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Heheh! Chiyori's special move, number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, well a chorizo is like a sausage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,and I thought that "chori"\Nsounds like "Chiyori."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness I'm Chiyori's LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have to feel guilty with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Heheheh! Chori-tto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:48.77,Main,,0,0,0,,May I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:53.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I-Iona...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Feverish Bond"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A city of mazes with no exit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the sound of bells ringing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave the "now" handed to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as I begin to walk in the morning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a world where light and dark intersect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}catharsis begins to awake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swore in my shaking heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I won't lose anyone anymore...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:05.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my tears flow tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll run through the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release myself towards the future I selected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to regain it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up on my wish{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I like Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Because Tama is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because Tama was with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Using me as a clue to find Tama is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.09,0:23:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I liked battling alongside Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything. Even about Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I... want to meet Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Accidental Reunion"\NThat Accidental Reunion.
